      "title": "Second language writing",
      "abstract": "Series Editor's preface Preface Acknowledgments 1. Writing and teaching writing 2. Second language writers 3. Syllabus design and lesson planning 4. Texts and materials in the writing class 5. Tasks in the L2 writing class 6. New technologies in writing instruction 7. Responding to student writing 8. Assessing student writing 9. Researching writing and writers Reference Index."
